column1: #Text=Haldia is a port and industrial city in Southwest Bengal in India .
#Text=Haldia is located near the confluence of the Hooghly River , a distributary of the Ganges and Haldi River .
#Text=Haldia Dock Complex , which is administratively a part of Kolkata Port Trust was commissioned in 1977 .
#Text=Haldia Refinery of Indian Oil Corporation was commissioned in 1975 .
#Text=Thereafter many industries cropped up in Haldia , including Haldia Petro-chemical complex .
